      <span class="cta-box__eyebrow">Final recommendation</span>
      <p class="cta-box__title">Termly — start free, upgrade to Pro+ when it actually matters</p>
      <p>If you're US-focused and document-hungry, the Free tier is a legitimate starting point. Plan to budget for Pro+ (~$15/month annual) before your traffic, EU ad revenue, or watermark visibility justifies the upgrade.</p>
